{"tid":617522,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"掟狗落街：救狗水警悼小白 「無諗過會令你更痛苦」","createTime":"2018-04-05T04:48:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-06T01:53:58.000Z","uid":130626,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"87ba8cb6949a08654e9d41292765669045c4abbb","tid":617522,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T04:48:35.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=OBFoKsiX%2BH3Sc29xeXp75ozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=325da5b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】銀狐犬「小白」4日前墮海，幸得水警及時到場營救，以為可逃過厄運，豈料竟遭人掟落街慘死。一位當日有份落水救起小白的水警，在fb留言悼念指：「當日我同你一個水泡兩條命，結果大家都可以脱險，但幾日後竟然...」<br />\n<br />\n他以為小白獲救後可重獲新生，回到主人身邊被寵愛，未料小白迎來第二次苦難，最終「救狗」一事反而令該水警倍感自責，他指：「人有第二次機會應該要好好珍惜，可惜你主人無把握，亦無珍惜你。同你短短相聚廿分鐘，連你叫咩名都唔知，只係叫你阿妹。阿妹對唔住，救你係我職責，但無諗過會令你更痛苦，我無勇氣打開新聞去見到你。希望你安息，佢一定會受到應得的懲罰。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Ut0BiadvEI.AvKFeH0LexA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/onccinstantnews.com/0f80f66c5dc828f250a517eced161ea0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FUt0BiadvEI.AvKFeH0LexA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2F0f80f66c5dc828f250a517eced161ea0&h=112f77db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%8E%9F%E7%8B%97%E8%90%BD%E8%A1%97-%E6%95%91%E7%8B%97%E6%B0%B4%E8%AD%A6%E6%82%BC%E5%B0%8F%E7%99%BD-%E7%84%A1%E8%AB%97%E9%81%8E%E6%9C%83%E4%BB%A4%E4%BD%A0%E6%9B%B4%E7%97%9B%E8%8B%A6-150922359.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%258E%259F%25E7%258B%2597%25E8%2590%25BD%25E8%25A1%2597-%25E6%2595%2591%25E7%258B%2597%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2582%25BC%25E5%25B0%258F%25E7%2599%25BD-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E8%25AB%2597%25E9%2581%258E%25E6%259C%2583%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E6%259B%25B4%25E7%2597%259B%25E8%258